channel.title: I need help with my server
channel.description: I have a runescape private server that runs on silab called radrs.sytes.net I own it as owner z but apparently it seems like i can only connect to it! i got a linksys router got the java and all the firewall parts set got it portforwarded and everything i need to. I havent had a actual person test it yet besides myself and i tried posting it on mopar server status and it says The server Radrs is offline, it must be online before you can register it here. I really need help on finding out how to get it online to other! i got no-ip all set up too! Signed Owner Z Aka Zaxwlyde
